						               													<description>Boss Monster offers players the chance to become the ultimate villain: the boss of their own sidescroller video game-style dungeon! For anyone who has ever spent hours navigating the pixelated perils of an 8-bit dungeon, Boss Monster is just the ticket! Up to six players lure hapless heroines into the self-made dungeon with the right treasures to devour their souls. But beware: the dungeon must be as deadly as it is alluring, or these puny invaders will survive long enough to reach the boss room and wound the boss monster. The best beast wins!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Boss Monster Big Box is the ultimate all-in-one package for fans of pixel dungeons and black humor. It includes, in addition to the base game, the expansions Next Level, Rise of the Minibosses, Total Destruction, and Vault of the Rogues. In addition, six dungeon tableaus are included to appropriately set the scene for the map dungeons.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
